===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} ''[[sceap|scēap]]'', from Germanic ''*skæpo-m''.  Cognate with Dutch ''[[schaap]]'', German ''[[Schaf]]'', and especially with West Frisian ''[[skiep]]'', including the undifferentiated plural.

